    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can bull rush an opponent straight to the ground.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Bull Rush, Merciless Rush, worshiper of Rovagug.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever you make a bull rush attack and your combat maneuver check exceeds the target's CMD by 5 or more, you can attempt to trip the target as part of your bull rush as a free action. This does not provoke an attack of opportunity.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>After succeeding at a bull rush combat maneuver check, you can spend 4 stamina points to attempt to trip the target with Squash Flat regardless of your bull rush combat maneuver check's result.",
